</pre></div><table class="mtq_answer_table"><colgroup><col class="mtq_oce_first" /></colgroup><tr id="mtq_row-3-1-1" onclick="mtq_button_click(3,1,1)" class="mtq_clickable"><td class="mtq_letter_button_td"><div id="mtq_button-3-1-1" class="mtq_css_letter_button mtq_letter_button_0" alt="Question 3, Choice 1">A</div><div id="mtq_marker-3-1-1" class="mtq_marker mtq_wrong_marker" alt="Wrong"></div></td><td class="mtq_answer_td"><div id="mtq_answer_text-3-1-1" class="mtq_answer_text">Temperature in Fahrenheit is 41.00</div></td></tr><tr id="mtq_row-3-2-1" onclick="mtq_button_click(3,2,1)" class="mtq_clickable"><td class="mtq_letter_button_td"><div id="mtq_button-3-2-1" class="mtq_css_letter_button mtq_letter_button_1" alt="Question 3, Choice 2">B</div><div id="mtq_marker-3-2-1" class="mtq_marker mtq_correct_marker" alt="Correct"></div></td><td class="mtq_answer_td"><div id="mtq_answer_text-3-2-1" class="mtq_answer_text">Temperature in Fahrenheit is 37.00</div></td></tr><tr id="mtq_row-3-3-1" onclick="mtq_button_click(3,3,1)" class="mtq_clickable"><td class="mtq_letter_button_td"><div id="mtq_button-3-3-1" class="mtq_css_letter_button mtq_letter_button_2" alt="Question 3, Choice 3">C</div><div id="mtq_marker-3-3-1" class="mtq_marker mtq_wrong_marker" alt="Wrong"></div></td><td class="mtq_answer_td"><div id="mtq_answer_text-3-3-1" class="mtq_answer_text">Temperature in Fahrenheit is 0.00</div></td></tr><tr id="mtq_row-3-4-1" onclick="mtq_button_click(3,4,1)" class="mtq_clickable"><td class="mtq_letter_button_td"><div id="mtq_button-3-4-1" class="mtq_css_letter_button mtq_letter_button_3" alt="Question 3, Choice 4">D</div><div id="mtq_marker-3-4-1" class="mtq_marker mtq_wrong_marker" alt="Wrong"></div></td><td class="mtq_answer_td"><div id="mtq_answer_text-3-4-1" class="mtq_answer_text">Compiler Error</div></td></tr></table><b><a>Data Types</a>    </b><br><b><a>Discuss it</a></b></br><br></br><div id="mtq_question_explanation-3-1" class="mtq_explanation"><div class="mtq_explanation-label">Question 3 Explanation: </div><div class="mtq_explanation-text"> Since 9 and 5 are integers, integer arithmetic happens in subexpression (9/5) and we get 1 as its value.

